networking-api-v1-draft 0.0.1.19 API

carttemplate

Overview

A proof-of-concept mod made for Fabric API Networking API v1 pull request.

Usage

Find it on Bintray

In build.gradle:

repositories {
    maven {
        url = "https://dl.bintray.com/liachmodded/doublecart"
    }
}

dependencies {
    modApi "io.github.fablabsmc.fablabs:networking-api-v1-draft:<your desired version>"
}
